class_description:
Thrown when an application tries to access an enum constant by name
 and the enum type contains no constant with the specified name.
 This exception can be thrown by the API used to read annotations
 reflectively.

params.param_description: the type of the missing enum constant
the name of the missing enum constant

Methods.method_description:
Constructs an EnumConstantNotPresentException for the
 specified constant.

return_description: the name of the missing enum constant

Methods.method_description: Returns the name of the missing enum constant.

return_description: the type of the missing enum constant

Methods.method_description: Returns the type of the missing enum constant.
